Taa bedelkeeda, qaadashada remdesivir oo lagu wareejiyo xididka, oo ah analog nucleotide, ayaa lagu ogaaday inay saameyn ku yeelatay bukaanka COVID-19 ee Mareykanka.
Remdesivir waa daawo cusub oo ay soo saartay Gilead oo markii hore loo isticmaali jiray in lagu daaweeyo cudurrada Ebola iyo Marlburg.
Kadib, remdesivir ayaa sidoo kale lagu ogaaday inuu daaweyn karo fayrasyada kale ee hal-xariiqda RNA oo ay ku jiraan MERS iyo SARS.
Iyada oo ku saleysan natiijooyinka, Gilead waxay u gudbisay Shiinaha tallaalka si loogu tijaabiyo dadka qaba SARS-CoV-2, natiijooyinka ayaa la sugayaa iyadoo la sugayo daqiiqado badan.
