Wuxuu sheegay in subaggu uu weyn yahay, taas oo keenta in qiimaha subagga uu yaraado, taas oo marka ay dhammaadaan ay ku sii jiraan subag badan oo qallalan oo keenta in la dareemo in la waayey.
