Ansiimada loo yaqaan 'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2' (ACE2) waa kiimiko ku xidhan dusha (dusha sare ee unugyada) unugyada unugyada unugyada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerka angiotensin-II iyadoo la kordhinayo Ang ((1-7) taasoo ka dhigaysa daawo la isticmaali karo oo lagula dagaallamo cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii horudhac u ah is-difaacidda qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Dadka waxaa inta badan loo yaqaanaa hACE2.
Ansiimada loo yaqaan 'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2' waa zinc-ku-dheer oo ku jira metallloenzyme-ka oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada dhiigga iyo unugyada kale.
Borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin kidney amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 wuxuu maraa maqaarka jirka hal mar, iyadoo qaybaha muhiimka ah ee ACE2 ay ka muuqdaan dusha sare ee xididdada iyo xididdada kale.
Meelaha ugu sareeya ee ACE2 ee maqaarka lagu soo saaro waxaa ka hortagga ka dhiga kiimiko kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, ka dibna dareeraha borotiinka ayaa loo wareejiyaa dhiigga kadibna waxaa loo beddelaa dheecaan.
ACE2 waxaa laga helaa qaybaha badan ee jirka: ACE2 waxay ku dhegan tahay maqaarka unugyada gaar ahaan qaybta II ee derbiyada unugyada, derbiyada yaryar, xididdada iyo unugyada xididdada dhiigga, iyo unugyada xididdada ee qaybaha badan ee jirka.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa unugyada maskaxda, qanjirka, hypothalamus, iyo xididada maskaxda.
Waxyaabaha ugu muhiimsan ee ACE2 waa in la hagaajiyo ACE
ACE waxay ku xidhan tahay hormoonka angiotensin I ee vasoconstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 ayaa isku xirta carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka timaada angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) oo lagu kala saaro angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku xirnaan kartaa silsilado kala duwan oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 ayaa sidoo kale maamusha isgaarsiinta unugyada ee loo yaqaan 'neutral amino acid SLC6A19' oo loo malaynayo inay keento cudurka Hartnup.
Maaddaama ay tahay borotiin la isugu gudbiyo unugyada, ACE2 waxay u shaqeysaa sidii marin weyn oo looga hortago fayraska corona qaar, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus oo keena SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus oo keena COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka 'spike S1 protein' ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ACE2 ee ugu muhiimsan ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada ayaa keena in fayraska iyo unugyada ay ka soo baxaan goobtooda oo ay dib ugu soo noqdaan qolalka unugyada.
Nidaamkan is-dhexgalka ayaa sidoo kale u baahan in la soo bandhigo borotiinka S iyo serine protease TMPRSS2, oo is-beddelka lagu baarayo si loo arko isticmaalka daaweynta. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ka mid ah ay ku qiyaasaan in hoos u dhigista heerka ACE2, ee unugyada, ay ka caawin karto la dagaallanka cudurka.
Taa bedelkeeda, hay'ado badan oo cilmi baaris iyo maamul ayaa taageeraya in la sii wado daweynta ACE inhibitor ee la yaqaan ARB.
