Sidoo kale, "sharxadda shuban biyoodka ayaa hoos u dhacday bukaanada la daaweeyay ACE inhibitors kuwaas oo u nugul shuban biyoodka, gaar ahaan kuwa is-go'aanka iyo wadnaha.
Isticmaalka xannibaadaha ACE ayaa sidoo kale loo maleynayay inay yareeyaan dhimashada cudurka shuban biyoodka, in kasta oo natiijooyinka aysan ahayn kuwo aad u daran marka loo eego khatarta cudurka shuban biyoodka"
ACE2 bini'aadamka ee isku dhafan (rhACE2) waxaa loo malaynayaa inuu yahay daaweynta ugu horreysa ee cudurka neefsashada ee ugu daran, waxaana la muujiyay inay hagaajinayso xajinta neefsashada iyo hawo qaadista neefta ee unugyada yaryar ee qaba cudurka neefsashada ee lipopolysaccharide-ku-saleysan.
Dhibaatada rhACE2 ee bini'aadamka waxay qaadataa 10 saacadood, waxqabadkuna wuxuu bilaabmaa 30 daqiiqo, oo ay ku jiraan waqtiga waxqabadka (mudada la isticmaalo) ee 24 saacadood.
Natiijooyinka laga helay daraasado kala duwan ayaa muujinaya in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay kuwa aan u adkeysan karin xakameynta nidaamka renin-angiotensin-ka (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurada ay ku kordhayaan wareegga angiotensin II. RhACE2 la buufiyey ayaa lagu baaray tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee daaweynta cudurada la xiriira cirbadaha.
