10 Abriil 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay ku dhawaaqeen inay iskaashi la yeelan doonaan taageerada barnaamijyada Bluetooth ee Android iyo iOS si toos ah barnaamijyadooda.
Shiinaha, dowladda Shiinaha, oo kaashanaysa shirkadda Alipau, ayaa soo saartay barnaamij u oggolaanaya muwaadiniinteeda inay hubiyaan haddii ay la kulmeen qof qaba COVID-19.
