Barnaamijka waxaa sameeyay IT-ga maxalliga ah, waxaana loo sameeyay si loo isticmaalo qof walba, waxaana loo xilsaaray dowladda. Waqooyiga Macedonia waxay soo bandhigtay barnaamijka "StopKorona!", barnaamijka Bluetooth si loo la socdo dadka la xiriira iyo dadka laga yaabo inay qabaan cudurka iyo in si dhakhso leh loo diro macluumaadka daryeelka caafimaadka iyo mas'uuliyiinta.
App-ka waxaa soo saaray Wasaaradda Isgaarsiinta iyo Teknolojiyada iyo Wasaaradda Caafimaadka.
Waxay imaan doontaa 14 Abriil 2020, iyadoo barnaamijyada ay weli sugayaan xaqiijinta dukaamada Google Play iyo Apple App Store.
12-kii Abriil, dowladda ayaa sheegtay in barnaamijka raadraaca xiriirka bukaanada uu ku jiro marxaladda ugu dambeysa ee horumarinta, waxaana la bilaabi doonaa toddobaadyo yar gudahood. App la mid ah ayaa laga soo saaray Ireland, iyo Faransiiska ("StopCovid").
Australia iyo New Zealand ayaa ka fikiraya barnaamijyada ku saleysan barnaamijka TraceTogether ee Singapore iyo borotokoolka BlueTrace. Ruushka ayaa qorsheynaya inuu soo bandhigo barnaamij geofencing ah oo loogu talagalay bukaannada COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, oo loogu talagalay in lagu hubiyo inaysan ka bixin guryahooda.
Ross Anderson, oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee jaamacadda Cambridge, ayaa soo bandhigay dhibaatooyinka ka dhalan kara barnaamijyada ku saleysan app-ka, oo ay ka mid yihiin in la qiyaaso inay si fiican u shaqeeyaan iyo in ay dhici karto in aysan shaqeyn haddii ay si fiican u shaqeeyaan marka ay isticmaalaan dadweynaha.
Si loo xaliyo dhibaatada barnaamijyada coronavirus ee been abuurka ah ama khatarta ah, Apple waxay xaddiday noocyada hay'adaha ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada la xiriira coronavirus-ka App Store, iyagoo oggolaanaya oo keliya kuwa la aqoonsan yahay ama la aqoonsan yahay.
