18-kii Maarso, WHO ayaa ku dhawaaqday in chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo la mid ah ay ka mid noqon doonaan afar nooc oo daawo ah oo la baaro oo qayb ka ah tijaabooyinka isdhexgalka.
Guddoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka gobolka New York ee chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso. 28-ka Maarso, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine sulfate iyo chloroquine phosphate iyadoo la raacayo oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah (Emergency Use Authorization, EUA).
Daawada weli ma aysan ansixin FDA-da tijaabooyinka caafimaad waxaana lagu ansixiyay EUA oo keliya sida daawo tijaabo ah oo loogu talagalay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee bukaannada la geliyey laakiin aan helin daaweyn tijaabo caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "isticmaalka, qiyaasta, ama muddada loo isticmaalo hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga daaweynta cudurka SARS-CoV-2" aan la garanayn.
Dhakhaatiirtu waxay sheegeen in ay isticmaaleen daawooyinkaas "oo aanay jirin wax kale oo ay sameeyeen".
